t. Combined, these venues allow the resort to host events of up to 1,000 guests, providing adaptable options for different formats and event concepts. Flexible event venues The resort's location further supports bleisure travel. Situated on Bac My An Beach and approximately 15 minutes from Danang International Airport and the city center, the property offers convenient access while maintaining a tranquil coastal setting. It is also within reach of key attractions such as the Golden Bridge \u2013 Ba Na Hills, renowned golf courses, and UNESCO World Heritage sites including Hoi An Ancient Town and My Son Sanctuary, allowing guests to extend their stay beyond business activities. Leisure facilities designed for relaxation and wellness Complementing its business and location advantages, the resort offers a range of leisure facilities designed for relaxation and wellness . These include a newly developed sports complex with tennis, pickleball, and padel courts, water sports activities, and a 24/7 fitness center. Spa services are also available, providing additional options for recovery and relaxation. Dining is an integral part of the experience, with three restaurants and a bar offering options from casual meals to beachfront evenings. Supported by an experienced hospitality team focused on continuously enhancing service standards, Pullman Danang Beach Resort continues to position itself as a destination where business and leisure travel can be seamlessly combined. Press kit & photos: download here For more information and bookings: diem.huynh@accor.com Website: https://www.pullman-danang.com/", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["spa services", "sports complex", "pullman danang beach resort", "beachfront resort", "responds", "fitness center", "mice infrastructure"], "creator": null, "language": "english", "country": ["qatar", "brunei", "turkmenistan", "vietnam", "azerbaijan", "timor-leste", "tajikistan", "turkey", "syria", "uzbekistan", "bhutan", "